## Setting up your environment

To get started deploying smart contracts on Liberty Chain, you need:

```bash
npm install @libertychain/sdk
```

Then configure your `hardhat.config.ts`:

```typescript
import { HardhatUserConfig } from "hardhat/config";

const config: HardhatUserConfig = {
  networks: {
    liberty: {
      url: "https://rpc.libertychain.org",
      chainId: 1337,
    },
  },
};

export default config;
```

What questions do you have? Happy to help!
